timelineItems.desc: Dan Haiek and Armchair Analyst Matt Doyle preview the one and only 2014 regular season meeting between the Philadelphia Union and Real Salt Lake. Will the well-oiled machine of Salt Lake get the better of the quickly gelling Philadelphia midfield? How does the Andrew Wenger acquisition impact this match?
